snippet.title: Split Fiction - Official Nintendo Switch 2 Announcement Trailer | Nintendo Switch 2 Direct
snippet.description:
Split Fiction is coming to Nintendo Switch 2! Get a look at some Split Fiction gameplay, ahead of the co-op game’s launch on June 5, 2025.

#SplitFiction #Gaming #Nintendo
